NAME
    Pod::Weaver::Plugin::Sort::Sub - Plugin to use when building
    Sort::Sub::* modules

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.005 of Pod::Weaver::Plugin::Sort::Sub
    (from Perl distribution Pod-Weaver-Plugin-Sort-Sub), released on
    2019-12-17.

SYNOPSIS
    In your weaver.ini:

     [-Sort::Sub]

DESCRIPTION
    This plugin is used when building distribution that contains
    "Sort::Sub::*" routines (see Sort::Sub::naturally for an example of such
    module; see also Sort::Sub). It currently does the following to
    lib/Sort/Sub/* .pm files:

    *   Add Synopsis section if not already exists

    *   Add description about the module to Description section

    *   Add Sort Arguments section containing list of sort arguments, from
        metadata

    *   Mention some modules in See Also section

        e.g. Sort::Sub.

